description: Stimulsoft Reports.Java is a Java based reporting tool which helps you create flexible and feature rich reports. All reports are created in a report designer with handy and user-friendly interface. Using Stimulsoft Reports.Java you can create reports on the basis of	various data sources. Rendered reports can be exported to different	formats.
